---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
const rawBase = import.meta.env.BASE_URL;
const baseUrl = rawBase.endsWith('/') ? rawBase.slice(0, -1) : rawBase;
---

<Layout>
  <section class="content_section" style="height:60%; margin-top:60px;">
      <div class="content">
          <h1 class="content_title">About Us</h1>
          <p class="content_text">
              Originally a shared dream of a few classmates, Okanagan Rover Craft was formally established in October
              of 2025, and has been firing on all cylinders ever since. Okanagan Rover Craft is composed of a
              community of young professionals with a team goal to build the best rover possible to compete at the
              Canadian International Robotics Challenge (CIRC). Okanagan Rover Craft is more than just a project, it’s
              an opportunity to build relationships, grow as professionals, and have fun. Okanagan Rover Craft is
              always looking for skilled and enthusiastic new members, reach out to us to learn more about the
              Okanagan Rovercraft team!
          </p>
          <div class="image-frame">
              <img src={`${baseUrl}/assets/images/IMG_1324.jpg`} alt="Group Photo" loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="expandable-image" />
          </div>
      </div>
  </section>
  <section class="content_section" id="get_involved" style="background-color:white; color:black; height:40%;">
      <div class="content" style="margin-top:-60px">
          <h2>How to get involved</h2>
          <p class="content_text">
              Looking to get involved in the future of Okanagan Rover Craft? We are always looking for passionate
              collaborators to join our mission. If you represent an organization looking to empower a team of young
              professionals, our outreach team would be thrilled to discuss the benefits of partnering with Okanagan
              Rover Craft with you! Sponsoring our team provides your organization with brand visibility while
              directly supporting our team's goals. A partnership with Okanagan Rover Craft allows you to connect with
              top student talent in STEM fields and support both our craft, and our team's future. If you are
              interested in supporting us, check out our sponsorship page!
          </p>
          <button class="learn-more" id="sponsor_button">
              Learn More
              <span class="arrow">→</span>
          </button>
      </div>
  </section>
</Layout>

<script>
  document.getElementById('sponsor_button')?.addEventListener('click', () => {
      window.location.href = `${import.meta.env.BASE_URL}sponsors/`;
  });
</script>
